      <p>
        The table below shows the estimated total employer cost for various RAL levels, assuming
        the standard INPS employer rate of 23.81%, TFR calculated per Article 2120 of the Civil
        Code, and an INAIL rate of 0.4% (office/service sector). For industries with a different
